Title: Performance Graphs of remote sites can not be embedded into PDF reports
Component: reporting
Class: bug
State: done
Date: 2015-02-25 14:49:46
Targetversion: 1.2.8

At the moment you can only access locally available graphs when drawing a PDF
report. If you like to create a PDF report of a host in a remote site including
graphs, you might solve this by creating the report on your remote site.

2016-02-08 23:17:37: changed state open -> done
Now with the new graphing system this is no problem anymore
